{"tid":1208381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學堂練左咁耐槍 今日終於可以打人","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T09:44:07.000Z","uid":195462,"like":3,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8f6c6905eb05d6957d11b7bb185b1b52ad60f0","tid":1208381,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"當年讀唔成書 唯有考警察<br />\n係學堂練左咁耐槍 畢左業都只係時不時靶場打下靶<br />\n悶到hihi <br />\n就算有d咩武裝練習 都係對住d同事同紙板扮野<br />\n今日終於可以同班友仔打過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當左咁耐差 真人真槍實彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下 舉咩旗呀 有人掟野呀<br />\n我開槍還擊之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打中頭? 梳li囉 你唔好彩關我鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好打死晒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他報警都冇用 冇人會處理<br />\n放膽去搶金行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3633a2056646ac977f3340ef785c5d66d0e3563","tid":1208381,"uid":201541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"你不如去食屎啦 學堂有無教"},{"pid":"9f16f7227d0189be0b86c9f168bbde9a064f3f6c","tid":1208381,"uid":199631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"唔洗理"},{"pid":"503a81a2bbe5a6673253504447e30ff2fb9751a1","tid":1208381,"uid":216477,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bc52d962dc396716ad313013ce9c653a7adb256","tid":1208381,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"D警犬係米大陸種黎 好9多新移民"},{"pid":"59c3bed96958ef9a0437a9c53b22e0dd2a5e9dcd","tid":1208381,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"見到有知名3毛會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都預左, 以閤下智商好難解釋<img src=\"/ass